item.title: CVE-2018-12244|2024-08-05T08:30:59.637Z -- symantec%20corporation -- symantec%20endpoint%20protection%20%28mac%20client%29
item.description: SEP (Mac client) prior to and including 12.1 RU6 MP9 and prior to 14.2 RU1 may be susceptible to a CSV/DDE injection (also known as formula injection) vulnerability, which is a type of issue whereby an application or website allows untrusted input into CSV files.
